Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.15,0:03:01.23,staff2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翻譯:Black 柿子 校對:深曉遊人 時間軸:錄音 後期:電子騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.57,0:03:05.06,tittle,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(761,192)}「不變的人流逝的時間」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.86,0:03:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果堂鄉的戀愛還是沒戲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.05,0:03:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 他連告白都辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.25,0:03:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他完全沒有氣餒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.03,0:03:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不合格
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.53,0:03:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總感覺是因為我們搞錯了時間的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.98,0:03:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.12,0:03:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天發生了好多事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.24,0:03:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 小啪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.59,0:03:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 今天早上我碰到了志保美小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.75,0:03:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.84,0:03:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說志保美小姐跟保幌小姐住在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.97,0:03:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們聊天時發現好像很談得來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.95,0:03:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是讓人吃驚的新聞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.95,0:03:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是志保美小姐和保幌小姐…很難想像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.31,0:03:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.92,0:03:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們之間發生了什麼事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.41,0:03:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.43,0:04:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們以前喜歡上了同一個男人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.29,0:04:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不知何時她們放下了憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.04,0:04:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,締結了深刻的友情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.14,0:04:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.05,0:04:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.66,0:04:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在保幌小姐家就可以從早到晚盡情地吃大阪燒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.51,0:04:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概瞄準了這個目的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.27,0:04:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 不可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.21,0:04:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是今後說不定什麼時候都能見到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.83,0:04:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 小啪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.81,0:04:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.91,0:04:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初中的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.53,0:04:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在圖書館裏偶然發現了天空的影集
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.37,0:04:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了天空也有各種各樣的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.95,0:04:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了之後連心情也變得柔和了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.92,0:04:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有種很懷念的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.48,0:04:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照片真的很神奇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.53,0:04:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我與志保美小姐的相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.27,0:05:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 小町 讓你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.45,0:05:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼早熟女會在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.71,0:05:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且這算什麼 「老闆 老樣子」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.33,0:05:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的常客的氣氛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.55,0:05:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.76,0:05:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近確實是常客
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.08,0:05:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是為了學拍照來與小啪競爭小香嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.25,0:05:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是複雜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.86,0:05:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小町也是不用數碼相機而用膠片機拍的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.10,0:05:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺把以前的照相機給了我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.51,0:05:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想看看你的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.88,0:05:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜歡哦 小町的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.83,0:05:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以是可以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.90,0:05:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺可愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.86,0:05:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是拍得很好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.94,0:06:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.84,0:06:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.74,0:06:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有各種各樣的照片 飽眼福了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.09,0:06:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然最開始全是小香的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.72,0:06:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.43,0:06:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.84,0:06:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近倒是多了風景照
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.33,0:06:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為很有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.58,0:06:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全愛上了拍照
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.32,0:06:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為覺得放在玉響店裏的姐姐所拍的照片很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.97,0:06:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.47,0:06:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 小薰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.39,0:06:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小啪憧憬志保美小姐的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.79,0:06:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小町又說小啪的照片很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.70,0:06:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連在一起了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.15,0:06:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 小楓的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.68,0:07:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.83,0:07:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憧憬之街時候的照片？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.21,0:07:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有這些 還有之前的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.25,0:07:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這些照片給志保美小姐看看怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.68,0:07:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得離得那麼近
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.64,0:07:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes 去吧去吧 大阪燒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.50,0:07:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰碳 Nice
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.68,0:07:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別叫我薰碳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.55,0:07:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小啪的照片可比大阪燒…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.72,0:07:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.96,0:07:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在意保幌小姐和志保美小姐的關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.56,0:07:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個麼…也算
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.88,0:07:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟平常一樣燒就行了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.40,0:07:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.17,0:07:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.42,0:07:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍下完美鏡頭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.84,0:07:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.27,0:07:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.06,0:07:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.45,0:07:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.32,0:07:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.57,0:07:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定這樣也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.27,0:08:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確好像很談得來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.31,0:08:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志保美小姐是專業的攝影師吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.09,0:08:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.00,0:08:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱乎乎的大阪燒真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.66,0:08:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.88,0:08:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 現在開始與保幌小姐的利比亞競猜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.28,0:08:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.01,0:08:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是突然的展開
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.49,0:08:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一問 請問保幌小姐的真名是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.88,0:08:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前保幌小姐的前輩有叫過她千茂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.94,0:08:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千茂 真是溫馨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.67,0:08:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 你們都知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.76,0:08:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二問 請問姓氏是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.95,0:08:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.03,0:08:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.41,0:08:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都認輸了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.48,0:08:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正確答案是數字的八和色彩的色 讀作YAKUSA
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.21,0:08:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.30,0:08:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YAKUSA 我們會小心不要念錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.42,0:09:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三問 請問為什麼店名叫「保幌」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.86,0:09:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「保幌」是廣島方言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.48,0:09:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起「賣保幌」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.48,0:09:13.32,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（ほぼろを賣る：把菜之類放進竹籠本是家務需要之一 賣籠子就等於新娘沒必要做家務了 也就是分開了）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.84,0:09:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是指新娘回娘家 也就是離婚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.44,0:09:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.86,0:09:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要取這種名字
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.43,0:09:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這家店的名字是取自保幌島的保幌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.32,0:09:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保幌島？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.63,0:09:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說保幌島是這附近的一座無人島
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.38,0:09:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生活在那裏的昆蟲漸漸地把島吃光了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.23,0:09:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在島已經不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.75,0:09:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺很感動呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.39,0:09:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能明白 很感動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.54,0:09:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.49,0:09:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.48,0:09:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是談得來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.99,0:09:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.52,0:09:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.76,0:09:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感冒好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.78,0:09:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為想吃保幌燒 所以靠氣勢治好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.65,0:10:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請來三份保幌燒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.53,0:10:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 保幌燒三人份
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.16,0:10:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 可以讓我拍幾張照片嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 那可真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.19,0:10:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就有勞這位美人小姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.31,0:10:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.23,0:10:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.54,0:10:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二 大阪燒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.92,0:10:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很美的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.57,0:10:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一張好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.73,0:10:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是天空的照片她也拍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.40,0:10:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 大阪燒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.16,0:10:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.69,0:10:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.52,0:10:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.85,0:10:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺每張都很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.51,0:10:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.15,0:11:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定澤渡小姐已經成了這座小鎮的居民了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.73,0:11:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是居住在這裏 變得瞭解這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.23,0:11:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜愛的地方不斷地增加
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.97,0:11:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以會更加 更加地想拍照
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.60,0:11:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 志保美小姐會拍各種不同的照片呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.84,0:11:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為志保美小姐只拍天空的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.79,0:11:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就覺得我也要找到那種目標才行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.50,0:11:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.36,0:11:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢 現在沒拍天空了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.62,0:11:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有目的地的車票
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.50,0:11:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帶在身上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.47,0:12:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志保美小姐給我的 沒有目的地的水色車票
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.40,0:12:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是夢想還未成形的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.70,0:12:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是志保美小姐說現在這樣就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.96,0:12:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定志保美小姐也會迷茫和躊躇嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.41,0:12:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 澤渡小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.47,0:12:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次一起去卡薩布蘭卡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.01,0:12:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡薩布蘭卡是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.93,0:12:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我們前輩開的店子 在吳市的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.39,0:12:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.77,0:12:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次跟理穗一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.29,0:12:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 肯定很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.77,0:12:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.23,0:12:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決定了 一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.75,0:12:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡薩布蘭卡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.36,0:12:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.65,0:12:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？那麼澤渡小姐那時候見過前輩了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.93,0:12:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 雖然是學插畫的 但是現在在經營咖啡屋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.64,0:13:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個怎麼說呢 應該說是自由吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.83,0:13:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從千茂小姐那裏聽說了這個 怎麼都想要見一面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.16,0:13:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志保美小姐 難道打算放棄攝影嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.41,0:13:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於新甜點的主意 我也好想從前輩那裏得到意見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.70,0:13:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天氣這麼好真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.01,0:13:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有這種事 一定是我想多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.19,0:13:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 等好久了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.24,0:13:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.53,0:13:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了 被前輩拜託去買冷面的材料了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.62,0:13:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生奶油？ 做冷面？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.07,0:13:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到達
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.58,0:13:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨卡薩布蘭…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.37,0:13:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千茂醬 你來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.13,0:14:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.66,0:14:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美園小姐 一直好想見你 好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.60,0:14:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎 千茂家的攝影師小姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.51,0:14:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是志保美理穗 初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.99,0:14:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是富士美園 初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.89,0:14:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是上次在竹原…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.36,0:14:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫澤渡楓 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.51,0:14:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對 小楓 歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.74,0:14:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候真的受大家照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.52,0:14:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.44,0:14:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為不知道去我家的路 大家帶她過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.09,0:14:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些 都是同一個地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.45,0:14:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我喜歡的地方哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.21,0:15:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到卡薩布蘭卡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.38,0:15:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 應戰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.83,0:15:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡薩布蘭卡基本菜譜候補的苦瓜奶油抹茶冷面 歡迎品嚐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.32,0:15:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苦瓜奶油抹茶冷面？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.83,0:15:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才要買生奶油
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.34,0:15:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來來 請吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.10,0:15:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要接受挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.77,0:15:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.15,0:15:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.39,0:15:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.18,0:15:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難以挑戰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.39,0:15:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝款待
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.26,0:15:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然苦瓜和生奶油不應該放一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.08,0:16:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.78,0:16:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是實驗菜譜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.58,0:16:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了新菜譜一直幫我試吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.71,0:16:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次會有怎樣奇怪的菜品呢 真期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.42,0:16:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一段時間不來挑戰下 身體反而不舒服了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.35,0:16:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.48,0:16:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的是呢 下次要做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.63,0:16:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多主意涌出來…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.92,0:16:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有新菜譜的主意了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.80,0:16:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.69,0:16:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放馬過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.65,0:16:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們就好好期待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.06,0:16:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼大家慢慢享受
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.46,0:16:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛的人 叫白井健
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.20,0:16:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在這個鎮上開花店
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.34,0:17:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健先生多年來一直在拍攝從同一個地方看到的風景
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.29,0:17:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他給我看這些照片時 也就明白了要一直住在這裏的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.72,0:17:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得真不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.27,0:17:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照片裏不僅是風景 變換的時間也拍了下來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.14,0:17:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想畫出不在這裏就畫不出來的畫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.91,0:17:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以回到這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.46,0:17:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美園小姐是千茂插畫學校的前輩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.12,0:17:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 出了學校後不久 就去京都畫插畫了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.87,0:17:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從千茂那裏聽說 美園小姐的插畫刊登在很多雜誌上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.20,0:17:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本以為前輩會一直從事插畫的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.79,0:17:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是千茂醬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.79,0:17:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到她想要開大阪燒 很吃驚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.81,0:18:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放棄了插畫的工作 馬上就開了破破幌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.81,0:18:02.95,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（店名讀音為hoboro 因為跟表示破爛不堪的boroboro讀音相近 所以前輩讀錯了）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.33,0:18:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是保幌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.38,0:18:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 保幌保幌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.37,0:18:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到前輩要回吳市的時候 覺得很可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.54,0:18:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果我也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.22,0:18:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃吃大阪燒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.46,0:18:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本想打掃店門卻和路過的人聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.40,0:18:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著小孩子慢慢長大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.76,0:18:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的生活真的很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.38,0:18:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 這是夢想改變了是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.65,0:18:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其說改變 不如說貪婪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.54,0:18:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貪婪？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.73,0:18:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 我們是貪婪的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.85,0:18:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們想要一直看著這個小鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.62,0:18:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是改變還是不變的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.50,0:18:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要在這裏一直看著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.26,0:18:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 既然是貪婪的 也許又會想去做別的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.05,0:19:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時再期待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.45,0:19:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次什麼時候都可以來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.21,0:19:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.60,0:19:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.46,0:19:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到的甜點主意 馬上就嘗試著做做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.57,0:19:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好了我就去嘗嘗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.52,0:19:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.62,0:19:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我拍一張美園小姐和保幌小姐的照片吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.89,0:19:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍吧拍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.75,0:19:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 千茂醬也一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.31,0:19:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.37,0:19:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二 大阪…燒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.39,0:19:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美的天空啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.31,0:19:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.35,0:19:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保幌小姐 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.49,0:20:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家有好吃的醃菜 過來拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.53,0:20:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎 好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.99,0:20:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 你們先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.18,0:20:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.68,0:20:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還想拿去保幌那裏的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.75,0:20:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次的很好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.63,0:20:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.92,0:20:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可能也是貪婪的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.27,0:20:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像美園小姐和千茂那樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.03,0:20:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 家族和朋友 還有鎮上的風景
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.64,0:20:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.28,0:20:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法選擇一個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.22,0:20:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.24,0:20:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志保美小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.98,0:20:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.86,0:20:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.18,0:20:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說我沒有在拍天空的照片時
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.60,0:20:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澤渡小姐看起來很寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.34,0:20:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在想我可能要放棄攝影嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.95,0:20:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 有點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.05,0:21:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 志保美小姐的夢想是志保美小姐的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.86,0:21:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澤渡小姐如果放棄了攝影的話 我也會寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.00,0:21:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志保美小姐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.33,0:21:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是因為我喜歡澤渡小姐 是很自然的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.57,0:21:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都無法阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.03,0:21:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 做決定的是澤渡小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.21,0:21:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是誰都無法阻止的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.24,0:21:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.74,0:21:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為喜歡才有期待 才會失落
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.75,0:21:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是美園小姐和千茂現在也還是優秀的前輩和後輩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.78,0:21:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有不變的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.51,0:21:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.65,0:21:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定 是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.78,0:21:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 我們是貪婪的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.85,0:21:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.05,0:22:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 還不會放棄攝影的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.43,0:22:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志保美小姐接下來會拍怎樣的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.26,0:22:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做決定的是志保美小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.54,0:22:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 我也會一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.26,0:22:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒寫目的地的水色車票
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.70,0:22:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管何時 目的地都是自由的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.20,0:22:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決定那個目的地的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.54,0:22:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是 自己啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.82,0:24:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.50,0:24:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新品甜點
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.93,0:24:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹筍鬆餅
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.20,0:24:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請品嚐
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.39,0:24:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外表雖然很樸素
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.21,0:24:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道很心動的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.61,0:24:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.37,0:24:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 玉響~Hitotose~
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.65,0:24:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「桃貓大人的憂鬱」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.17,0:24:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「失戀照相機」
