Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.61,0:23:32.49,ed cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,300)}請你如常
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.65,0:23:39.42,ed cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,300)}神有時會惡作劇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.73,0:23:52.27,ed cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,300)}讓人把最重要的事物棄之不顧
